<br>
I recently acquired the 65 earth pet and thought I was in for a treat.  Wrong.<br>
With the earth pets root, the mob always turns and attacks the hammer immediatly and the shaman pet as well., leaving the poor dps of the earth pet to do the damage.<br>
<br>
As for soloing, its bloody obvious that PoP is making that difficult at least under the traditional pet methods.<br>
<br>
Leaving me to ask... What am I supposed to do with this pet.  Soloing is too innefective to begin with (CotAM excluded from what I hear).  Duoing the earth pet root seems to give aggro to any other pet onthe mob.  And in groups or raids, no one wants a pet rooting for the same aggro messing reasons.<br>
<br>
What a waste of a rune.<br>
<br>
Good ol 61 air. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65160&amp;resize=true" target="top">Epicure</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
